{"tid":336844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（垃圾節目）中國好聲音撚入","createTime":"2017-07-26T18:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T09:44:58.000Z","uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba86959345781a9007b5e6d2b8a9ce705375c86","tid":336844,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"由第一季好聲音已經開始睇，一直到而家進化到新歌聲第二季<br />\n<br />\n質素可以話係一季比一季差，但並唔明顯，但去到新歌聲真係高下立見，穩第一季是但一個再參加應該都可以冠軍了<br />\n<br />\n睇完頭兩隻，無一個聽得落，稍為好聽少少得一個葉炫清同一個西藏老師<br />\n<br />\n下年係咪可以收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   好聲音可以講係伴住我成長 每年暑假既娛樂節目 而家就連睇導師搶人都好似無咁好睇"},{"pid":"d130c8ac79d06f16636876f4276cdaab8bab486e","tid":336844,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"今季 連續二個人都冇人簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7d1cf29c107dfbe9d89f436b8bc98509e6ba6f","tid":336844,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"同埋睇得出 好多唔搶專登讓人比佢"},{"pid":"6910e761934b155820bec73467af510bdabcdc18","tid":336844,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:19:13.000Z","msg":"以前播得既可以講係99%有導師揀<br />\n<br />\n今季第二集有3，4個無人揀，又唔係好聽都播出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735f54cde513172b43333804792f4a3010fe087e","tid":336844,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今季 連續二個人都冇人簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d有人揀既 都好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef0eb3ff156f99372166b95952c8d5a30d2566e","tid":336844,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}